**Spiritualist** | Townsfolk Power | Haunted
__Basics__
When the Spiritualist becomes a ghost, they can whisper to a living player each night.
__Details__
Each night, while they are a ghost, they may choose a player (immediate ability). For the rest of the night, as well as the following day, the Spiritualist may anonymously whisper with their target.
The Spiritualist may only pick each target once.

__Simplified__
After the Spiritualist dies, they can whisper to one player each night.

__Formalized__
Ghostly Role
Immediate Night: [Attribute: @Selection lacks `SpiritTouched`] {Direct} |spiritualist.1|
  • Conversation Reset `Spirit Touched`
  • Grant `Spirit Touched` to @Selection
  • Whisper to `Spirit Touched` as Corrupt Wolf (~NextDay)
  • Apply `SpiritTouched` to @Selection
Passive Start Night: Conversation Reset `Spirit Touched`

__Card__
The Spiritualist can whisper to the living while dead.
